Package: madlibr
Type: Package
Title: Easy Madlib-Style Formatting For Auto-Generated Text
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daniel Luckett
Maintainer: Daniel Luckett <daniel.luckett.work@gmail.com>
Description: When writing text for analytical reports, figure captions, and 
    dashboards, it is often necessary for text to adapt to statistics and 
    results. The madlib package solves this problem with a straightforward, 
    madlib-style interface.
